fulltitle: Michael Parenti: Capitalism as Totalitarian Social Order (KPFA, 1993)
title: Michael Parenti: Capitalism as Totalitarian Social Order (KPFA, 1993)
_filename: _Michael Parenti - Capitalism as Totalitarian Social Order (KPFA, 1993).mp4
description:
Political analysis Michael Parenti discusses the relationship of capitalism and the social structure. He analyzes the role of the media in maintaining the private power elite, how private research is funded by public funds, and the nature of the plutocracy.

Interviewed by Philip Maldari and Kris Welsh
Recorded: KPFA, 16 Feb. 1993.
